<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/10975-4049">fverd</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">4 hours ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">President Obama's certificate of Birth, demonstrates that 1. he was born, 2. that he was born somewhere other than a hospital, 3. probably without a doctor or registered nurse, 4. verified with a laser certificate that did not exist at the time of his birth.  So, where was he actually born, and at what hospital and who was the attending physician?</div>
