<div id="Idea_3543"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/3543-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_3543">Automatic Saving and Storage of E-mails and other Electronic Records in their Original Format&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/3967-4049">Sunshine in Government Initiative </a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">4 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">The federal government can become more environmentally friendly and more efficient by taking the relatively undemanding step of creating a system which automatically saves, catalogues and organizes all electronically created records in electronic format.</div>
